---
interface Props {}
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";

const {} = Astro.props;
---

<div class="project-wrapper">
  <div class="project-description">
    <div>
      <h1>Product/UI/UX @ Curant</h1>
      <div>
        <p>
          <a
            class="link-styling"
            href="https://curant/curant.io"
            target="_blank">Curant (formerly Freightpay)</a
          >
        </p>
        <p>Product, Design, & Management</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-wrapper">
      <p>
        As the sole designer at Curant, I think it is crucial for me to shape
        the product holistically. This involves everything from user interface,
        product perception through marketing, and customer support and
        documentation.<br /><br />Additionally, internal users shouldn't be
        neglected either. It is crucial for sole product designers to support
        the engineering team through QA and documentation efforts.
        <br />
        <br />
         The section ahead showcases what I've done at Curant.
        <br />
         If you'd like to see a deeper glimpse at my design & process, feel free
        to skip ahead to <a class="link-styling" href="#paymentforms"
          >Payment Forms</a
        > or the <a class="link-styling" href="#widgetlibrary">Widget Library</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="section-header"><h2>key milestones</h2></div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="section-wrapper">
        <div class="half">
          <h3>Curant's 2022 year in review</h3>
          <img
            class="pop-image project-image border rounded-corners"
            src="/curant/curant_year-in-review.png"
            alt="Curant's 2022 year in review"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="half">
          <h3>From $0 to over $12 million in transactions</h3>
          <img class="project-image" src="https://placehold.co/160x100/" />
          <img class="project-image" src="https://placehold.co/160x100/" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="section-header"><h2>redesign</h2></div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <div>
        <h3>Modernization, brand standardization, and product scalability</h3>
        <div class="section-wrapper">
          <div class="forth">
            <img
              class="pop-image project-image rounded-corners"
              src="/curant/curant_redesign-old.png"
              alt="Curant's old app design"
              style="max-width:270px;"
            />
            <div class="caption-wrapper">
              <p class="caption">
                <em>old app design&nbsp;</em>
                <Icon class="icon" name="ic:outline-arrow-upward" />
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="three-forths">
            <div class="caption-wrapper">
              <Icon
                class="icon"
                name="ic:outline-arrow-downward"
                style="margin-bottom:8px;"
              /><p class="caption" style="margin-top:-4px">
                <em>&nbsp;refreshed app design, branding, and components</em>
              </p>
            </div>
            <img
              class="pop-image project-image rounded-corners"
              src="/curant/curant_redesign-new.png"
              alt="Curant's redesigned app, branding, and components"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="section-header"><h2>marketing</h2></div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <div>
        <h3>
          Website Launch to capture new leads // In collaboration with <a
            class="link-styling"
            href="https://www.jessebutts.com/"
            target="_blank"
            style="font-weight:600;">Jesse Butts</a
          >
        </h3>
        <img
          class="pop-image project-image rounded-corners"
          src="/curant/curant_marketing-website.png"
          alt="Curant's Website"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>
          Campaign to connect and meet people at FreightWaves F3 Future of
          Freight Festival
        </h3>
        <img
          class="pop-image project-image rounded-corners"
          src="/curant/curant_marketing-freightwaves.png"
          alt="FreightWaves F3 x Freightpay campaign website and LinkedIn posts"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>
          Mini Newsletter series to keep our existing users engaged & informed
        </h3>
        <img
          class="pop-image project-image rounded-corners"
          src="/curant/curant_marketing-newsletters.png"
          alt="Newsletter emails sent to Curant customers"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Pitch decks for Customers, & Investors</h3>
        <img
          class="pop-image project-image rounded-corners"
          src="/curant/curant_marketing-decks.png"
          alt="Pitch deck slides for customers & investors"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="section-header"><h2>cx & support</h2></div>
    <div class="section-wrapper">
      <div class="half">
        <h3>Collaborative customer onboarding checklists on Trello</h3>
        <img
          class="pop-image project-image rounded-corners"
          src="/curant/curant_customer-onboarding.png"
          alt="The Trello Board for customer onboarding"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="half">
        <h3>Documentation & Support for new features</h3>
        <img
          class="pop-image project-image rounded-corners"
          src="/curant/curant_customer-support.png"
          alt="Documentation & support for customers"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="section-header"><h2>internal</h2></div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="section-wrapper">
        <div class="half">
          <h3>Launched a temporary QA process to define release priorties</h3>
          <img
            class="pop-image project-image rounded-corners"
            src="/curant/curant_internal-qa.png"
            alt="QA process"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="half">
          <h3>Design Spikes leading to new features</h3>
          <img
            class="pop-image project-image rounded-corners"
            src="/curant/curant_internal-spikes.png"
            alt="Design Spikes: Documentation, Research, and early Design mocks"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style></style>
</div>
